The exact v1.3.0 source is preserved at [automation-review-authorization-ci-boundary.md in parent commit `24b7b79b`](https://github.com/HomericIntelligence/Mnemosyne/blob/24b7b79b78b99da58318adb52dcdcf5f8166b52e/skills/automation-review-authorization-ci-boundary.md).

